Dispatch Class-1. Ambulansya.

00:39:29.930 --> 00:39:32.920
Unibersidad ng Keihin, larangan ng Kanazawa Campus,

00:39:32.920 --> 00:39:35.630
2-8-16, Shiura, Kanazawa Ward.

00:39:35.630 --> 00:39:39.160
Pagpapadala ng Kanazawa Paramedic Squad 1.
[Kanazawa 1]

